| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1046 — Recovery Inhibition (anubis)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4851aaaa-9c8a-5be8-ae42-8ed2a9a4ee6b"
